      <title>美国和伊朗之间的战争扩大，袭击遍及整个地区</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/world/middleeast/us-iran-war-strikes-infrastructure-civilians.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗官方媒体的视频和报道显示桥梁、铁路和其他基础设施遭到破坏。美国在该地区的盟友报告称伊朗发动了报复性袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/world/middleeast/us-iran-war-strikes-infrastructure-civilians.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 21:49:49 GMT</pubDate>
