    <item>
      <title>中国的人工智能登月计划推出基米模型，威胁美国的领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/business/china-ai-moonshot-kimi.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的Moonshot AI推出了一种免费的人工智能模型，该模型似乎缩小了与美国科技公司尖端产品的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/business/china-ai-moonshot-kimi.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 20:04:57 GMT</pubDate>
